<HEADLINE>
Flamengo goalkeeper investigated for disappearance of ex-
girlfriend
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
RIO DE JANEIRO, June 26 (Xinhua)
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Flamengo star goalkeeper Bruno was being investigated over the loss of his ex-
girlfriend.
</P>
<P>
Eliza Samudio, Bruno's ex-girlfriend and his 4-month-old baby boy's mother,
disappeared from her hometown of Belo Horizonte, Minas Gerais.
</P>
<P>
According to special agent Alessandra Wilke who is handling the case, Samudio
was beaten in a property owned by Bruno in the interior of Minas Gerais. Since
last Wednesday, no one has heard from Samudio, leading police to believe that a
homicide has taken place.
</P>
<P>
Wilke said that Bruno will be brought in for questioning.
</P>
